correct and based upon logic. 

Whether a clone could commit suicide is entirely based upon the personal
belief of the individual before he/she is clone.  Clones of some people
will voluntarily die off, clones of other people would not. I for one have
trouble just keeping the original of me from voluntarily dying off.

As they say, results may vary.

